-   Click the green "use template" button to make a repository with this content. Make sure to make your repo public (since GitHub Pages doesn't work on private repos unless you have a paid account) and check box to include all the branches (so that you get the gh-pages branch). <img src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2545978/197051535-c43c62de-17e8-40bf-a536-3eea8db250c4.png" alt="image" width="637"/>

